divs: Sighting Detailsthis was the best sighting of all the ufos that I've witnessed this object flew over my house i wish i would've taken a photo this object was moving fairly quick and the lights were flashing in a slow strange pattern that went all the away around it i know it wasn't a plane or a helicopter the object flew across the sky with no noise at all it was strange but not alarming i haven't seen this object since.
Summary: strange object with yellow flashing lights circling all the away around it
